Open OpenGL folder from the downloaded file
Location May vary from "Program files" to "Program filesx86"
Copy the glut.h file and paste to the folder “C:\Program Files\CodeBlocks\MinGW\include\GL“.
Open lib folder from downloaded file.
Copy glut32.lib and glut.def and paste to the folder “C:\Program Files\CodeBlocks\MinGW\lib“.
Open bin folder from the downloaded file.
Copy the glut.dll file and paste to the folder “C:\Windows\System32" as well as in SYSWOW64(It doesn't matter You are using 64-Bit or 32-Bit).
You are done and ready to go.
